00:42:14,870 --> 00:42:20,960
♫  You are the stranger I want to know  ♫

460
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:24,870
♫  Don't let me go  ♫

461
00:42:24,870 --> 00:42:28,980
♫  I will do little tricks for you  ♫

462
00:42:30,080 --> 00:42:36,180
♫  Don't bury your secret heart  ♫

